Scenario: Success Create Equipment Inspection Form


  Given the user opens the Equipment Inspection menu
  Then the Equipment Inspection page displays the list of previous submissions

  When the user taps the New Submission button
  Then the app opens the Equipment Inspection form page

  When the app requests the form schema from the server
  Then the dynamic form fields are loaded based on the form code

  Then the Form Code field is displayed correctly at the top of the form

  When the user inputs text into any text fields
  Then the text fields accept the input with no issues

  When the user selects a date from the Date Picker
  Then the selected date appears correctly in the field

  When the user opens any dropdown/select field
  Then the dropdown shows the correct options and the user can select one option

  When the user taps on a radio button option
  Then only one radio option is selected at a time

  When the user taps the Image Picker field
  Then the camera or gallery opens successfully

  When the user chooses or captures an image
  Then the selected image preview appears in the field

  When the user fills all required fields
  Then required fields show validation messages if left empty

  When the user submits the form
  Then the app validates all fields and no errors are shown

  When the app sends the submission to the server
  Then the API request is successful and the form is stored

  Then the user is redirected back to the submission list
  And the newly submitted form appears with the correct timestamp

  When the user closes and reopens the app
  Then all previously submitted data is still available and loaded correctly
